      "text": [
        "382 - وَقَالَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «مَنْ عَدَّ غَداً مِنْ أَجَلِهِ فَقَدْ أَسَاءَ صُحْبَةَ اَلْمَوْتِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.382 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said: \"Whoever considers tomorrow as part of their lifespan has not kept good company with death.\""
        ]
      }
    }
